<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>文章 on Ivo's Inkwell</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/</link><description>Recent content in 文章 on Ivo's Inkwell</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 Ivo</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>从Firefox ESR 更换至 Zen</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/from-firefox-esr-change-to-zen-broswer/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/from-firefox-esr-change-to-zen-broswer/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;安全，简洁是我对于浏览器的一个认知，之前使用Chrome也是因为这个原因，当时Chrome相比于微软家的Edge有一种简洁的美，但是后来是因为书签同步问题选择了Firefox，后来发现ESR版本新功能更少更简洁，于是换成了Firefox ESR。&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/from-firefox-esr-change-to-zen-broswer/featured.png"/></item><item><title>迁移至PVE</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/migrate-to-pve/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/migrate-to-pve/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;相关原因
